            <Paragraphs>
              <Paragraph>
                <TextRuns>
                  <TextRun>
                    <Value EvaluationMode="Auto">Instructions:</Value>
                    <Style>
                      <FontFamily>Calibri</FontFamily>
                      <FontSize>11pt</FontSize>
                      <FontWeight>Bold</FontWeight>
                    </Style>
                  </TextRun>
                  <TextRun>
                    <Value EvaluationMode="Auto">
The 360 feedback form is used for development purposes only.  It has two key objectives: -
a) Help team members gain greater insight in to how their work behavior is perceived by other team members
b) Feedback received will be used by the team member to reinforce their strengths and close any gaps highlighted.

You have been selected to provide 360 feedbacks for the above named team member who values your perspective and input.  Using the scale below, kindly provide your personal assessment by indicating to what extent the team member exhibits the follow competences. Feedback provided will be confidential and anonymous. 

Evaluation Scale:-
5	Exceptional strength
4	Is a strength
3	Demonstrates capability
2	Development needed
1	Significantly needs development
N/A	Unable to assess</Value>
                    <Style>
                      <FontFamily>Calibri</FontFamily>
                      <FontSize>11pt</FontSize>
                    </Style>
                  </TextRun>
                  <TextRun>
                    <Value xml:space="preserve" EvaluationMode="Auto">
</Value>
                    <Style />
                  </TextRun>
                </TextRuns>
                <Style />
              </Paragraph>
            </Paragraphs>
